<body><div class="frame"><aside class="side"><div><a class="brand" href="/"><img src="/assets/logo/monogram.svg" alt=""><div><strong>Luanda Rodrigues,</strong><span>Data Analyst</span></div></a><div class="intro-card"><p>Brazilian data analyst connecting healthcare operations, BI, machine learning and decision intelligence.</p></div><div class="side-viz" aria-label="Abstract data visual"><canvas id="sideGraphCanvas"></canvas></div><div class="side-stats"><div class="stat"><strong>04</strong><span>cases</span></div><div class="stat"><strong>06</strong><span>layers</span></div><div class="stat"><strong>EN/PT</strong><span>site</span></div></div></div><div class="links"><a href="mailto:luandarodrigues30@gmail.com">Email <span>↗</span></a><a href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues">GitHub <span>↗</span></a><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/luanda-rodrigues">LinkedIn <span>↗</span></a><a href="/pt/">Português <span>↗</span></a></div></aside><main class="main"><nav class="topnav"><a href="#about">About</a><a href="#work">Work</a><a href="#method">Data Cloud</a><a href="#contact">Contact</a><a class="lang" href="/pt/">PT-BR</a></nav><section class="hero"><div><p class="eyebrow reveal">Health / Operations / Intelligence</p><h1 class="reveal">Turning complex systems into <em>readable data.</em></h1><div class="split reveal"><p>I build analytical work that connects hospital operations, public health data, SQL, BI, machine learning, graph analytics and decision communication.</p><div class="chips"><span class="chip">Brazilian</span><span class="chip">Remote</span><span class="chip">Relocation</span><span class="chip">Python</span><span class="chip">SQL</span><span class="chip">Power BI</span><span class="chip">NetworkX</span></div></div></div></section><section class="about section" id="about"><div><p class="eyebrow">About / Trajectory</p><h2>Engineering, healthcare and data in the same system.</h2></div><div class="about-copy"><p>My path started in Biomedical Engineering and moved into Hospital Management, where I learned to read operations as systems: flows, bottlenecks, indicators, risks and decisions.</p><p>At HC-UFU/EBSERH, I work close to clinical pharmacy operations, KPI monitoring and public healthcare routines. I also bring a digital layer from marketing technology, HTML email, content creation, design thinking and AI-supported workflows.</p><img class="about-photo" src="/assets/ChatGPT%20Image%2017%20de%20mai.%20de%202026%2C%2017_26_13.png" alt="Luanda Rodrigues working with a laptop"><div class="grid"><article class="box"><span>01</span><h3>Healthcare operations</h3><p>Clinical pharmacy workflows, hospital routines, public health data and service performance.</p></article><article class="box"><span>02</span><h3>Decision intelligence</h3><p>BI, KPIs, analytical models and communication for practical decisions.</p></article><article class="box"><span>03</span><h3>Technical stack</h3><p>Python, SQL, Power BI, machine learning, graph analytics and NLP.</p></article><article class="box"><span>04</span><h3>Brazilian context</h3><p>Brazilian professional available for remote roles and open to relocation.</p></article></div></div></section><section class="cloud-section" id="method"><div class="cloud-pin"><div class="cloud-copy"><p class="eyebrow">Scroll / Data Cloud</p><h2>From signals to decisions.</h2><p>This is closer to an Obsidian-style knowledge graph: many small notes orbit the large themes. Tap to shift between dispersed exploration and analytical clusters.</p><div class="actions"><button class="cloud-btn" id="shuffleCloud">Reshuffle graph</button><button class="cloud-btn secondary" id="clusterCloud">Cluster view</button></div></div><div class="cloud-stage" id="cloudStage"><canvas class="graph-canvas" id="graphCanvas"></canvas><div class="legend"><div class="legend-row"><span class="dot health"></span>Healthcare</div><div class="legend-row"><span class="dot models"></span>Models & NLP</div><div class="legend-row"><span class="dot ops"></span>BI & Operations</div></div></div></div></section><section class="tabs" id="work"><div class="title"><p class="eyebrow">Selected work</p><h2>Projects, method and stack in one interface.</h2></div><div class="tabbar"><button class="tabbtn active" data-tab="projects">Projects</button><button class="tabbtn" data-tab="methodtab">Method</button><button class="tabbtn" data-tab="stack">Stack</button><button class="tabbtn" data-tab="background">Background</button></div><div class="summary"><strong id="tabTitle">Projects</strong><p id="tabText">Public portfolio cases showing healthcare, machine learning, SQL, graphs, NLP and decision-oriented communication.</p></div><div class="panel active" id="projects"><article class="card"><span class="num">01</span><div><h3>Mapping Primary Healthcare Units in Brazil</h3><p>Geospatial and data governance analysis of 47,714 Brazilian Primary Healthcare Units. The project examines geographic distribution, coordinate quality, registry completeness and territorial coverage signals.</p><div class="project-meta"><div><span>Scope</span><strong>47,714 facilities</strong><small>Brazilian UBS records, location fields, regional distribution and public health infrastructure.</small></div><div><span>Method</span><strong>Geo + quality audit</strong><small>Coordinate validation, missingness checks, regional aggregation and map reading.</small></div><div><span>Decision value</span><strong>Coverage</strong><small>Supports prioritization, registry correction and territorial planning.</small></div></div><ul><li>Health Analytics</li><li>Geoanalysis</li><li>Data Quality</li><li>Public Health</li></ul></div><a href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues/luandarodrigues/tree/main/projects/ubs-healthcare-mapping">Open ↗</a></article><article class="card"><span class="num">02</span><div><h3>Heart Disease Risk Prediction</h3><p>Clinical machine learning project using 918 observations and 11 predictors to model heart disease risk while separating decision support from automated diagnosis.</p><div class="project-meta"><div><span>Scope</span><strong>Clinical data</strong><small>Age, symptoms, blood pressure, cholesterol, ECG, angina and ST-slope.</small></div><div><span>Method</span><strong>Responsible ML</strong><small>Validation, ROC-AUC, F1-score, confusion matrix and interpretation.</small></div><div><span>Decision value</span><strong>Triage</strong><small>Supports prioritization with clinical caution and ethical limits.</small></div></div><ul><li>Machine Learning</li><li>Clinical Risk</li><li>Scikit-learn</li><li>Responsible ML</li></ul></div><a href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues/luandarodrigues/tree/main/projects/heart-disease-risk-ml">Open ↗</a></article><article class="card"><span class="num">03</span><div><h3>Brazilian E-Commerce Delivery Experience</h3><p>Operational analytics with Olist to understand how delivery delay, freight, seller behavior, category and payment affect customer reviews.</p><div class="project-meta"><div><span>Scope</span><strong>99,441 orders</strong><small>Orders, items, sellers, payments, freight, reviews and delivery dates.</small></div><div><span>Method</span><strong>SQL + features</strong><small>Joins, delay variables, review score, seller/category cuts and KPIs.</small></div><div><span>Decision value</span><strong>Experience</strong><small>Shows where logistics friction affects satisfaction.</small></div></div><ul><li>SQL</li><li>Logistics</li><li>Customer Experience</li><li>Operational Analytics</li></ul></div><a href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues/luandarodrigues/tree/main/projects/olist-ecommerce-experience-analytics">Open ↗</a></article><article class="card"><span class="num">04</span><div><h3>CineGraph Network Intelligence</h3><p>Graph and NLP case connecting movies, TV shows, people, recommendations and reviews through relationships and text signals.</p><div class="project-meta"><div><span>Scope</span><strong>Graph media data</strong><small>22,393 movies, 15,562 TV shows, 58,393 people and reviews.</small></div><div><span>Method</span><strong>NetworkX + NLP</strong><small>Graph, nodes/edges, collaboration, TF-IDF and text signals.</small></div><div><span>Decision value</span><strong>Recommendation</strong><small>Supports discovery, clustering and recommender logic.</small></div></div><ul><li>NetworkX</li><li>NLP</li><li>Graphs</li><li>Recommender Systems</li></ul></div><a href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues/luandarodrigues/tree/main/projects/cinegraph-network-intelligence">Open ↗</a></article></div><div class="panel" id="methodtab"><div class="grid"><div class="box"><span>01</span><h3>Frame the decision</h3><p>Define the decision, users, metrics and risks before modeling.</p></div><div class="box"><span>02</span><h3>Audit the data</h3><p>Check granularity, keys, duplicates, nulls, outliers, dates and rules.</p></div><div class="box"><span>03</span><h3>Build the analytical layer</h3><p>Transform raw data into tables, indicators, features and visuals.</p></div><div class="box"><span>04</span><h3>Choose the method</h3><p>Use BI, statistics, ML, NLP or graphs depending on the problem.</p></div><div class="box"><span>05</span><h3>Interpret limits</h3><p>Separate signal from noise and show uncertainty, bias and limitations.</p></div><div class="box"><span>06</span><h3>Communicate for action</h3><p>Deliver analysis through narrative, README, dashboard or recommendation.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel" id="stack"><div class="grid"><div class="box"><span>Analysis</span><h3>Python · Pandas · NumPy</h3><p>Cleaning, exploration, missing values, features and consistency checks.</p></div><div class="box"><span>SQL & Data</span><h3>SQL · joins · relational modeling</h3><p>Analytical queries, CTEs, keys, granularity and datasets.</p></div><div class="box"><span>BI</span><h3>Power BI · Looker · KPIs</h3><p>Dashboards, indicators, monitoring and decision metrics.</p></div><div class="box"><span>Machine Learning</span><h3>Scikit-learn · ROC-AUC</h3><p>Classification, validation, model comparison and interpretation.</p></div><div class="box"><span>Graph & NLP</span><h3>NetworkX · TF-IDF · reviews</h3><p>Networks, relationships, recommendations and text mining.</p></div><div class="box"><span>Operations</span><h3>Healthcare · logistics · experience</h3><p>Flows, bottlenecks, delays, coverage and operational impact.</p></div></div></div><div class="panel" id="background"><div class="grid"><div class="box"><span>Healthcare</span><h3>Hospital operations</h3><p>Clinical pharmacy workflows, KPIs, public health data and decision support.</p></div><div class="box"><span>Education</span><h3>Biomedical Engineering + Hospital Management</h3><p>Systems thinking, healthcare technology and data analysis.</p></div><div class="box"><span>Public sector</span><h3>EBSERH · 5th place</h3><p>Brazilian public healthcare and hospital operations context.</p></div><div class="box"><span>Digital</span><h3>Marketing technology</h3><p>Content, design, HTML email, scientific communication, automation and AI.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="contact" id="contact"><div><p class="eyebrow">Contact</p><h2>Let’s connect data, operations and decisions.</h2><div class="contact-layout"><div><p class="note">Send a structured message directly from here. The form sends it to my inbox.</p><div class="row"><a class="btn" href="https://github.com/luandarodrigues">GitHub ↗</a><a class="btn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/luanda-rodrigues">LinkedIn ↗</a></div></div><form id="contactForm"><label for="name">Name</label><input id="name" placeholder="Your name" required><label for="company">Company</label><input id="company" placeholder="Company or organization"><label for="email">Email</label><input id="email" type="email" placeholder="you@email.com"><label for="message">Message</label><textarea id="message" placeholder="What would you like to discuss?" required></textarea><button type="submit">Send message ↗</button></form></div></div></section></main></div>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/gsap.min.js"></script><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script><script>
function initMiniGraph(){const c=document.getElementById('sideGraphCanvas');if(!c)return;const box=c.parentElement,ctx=c.getContext('2d');let w=0,h=0,dpr=1,pts=[];function size(){dpr=Math.min(devicePixelRatio||1,2);w=box.clientWidth;h=box.clientHeight;c.width=w*dpr;c.height=h*dpr;c.style.width=w+'px';c.style.height=h+'px';ctx.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0)}function reset(){size();pts=[];const hubs=[[.24,.34,'#d7ff6f'],[.62,.43,'#9fc8ff'],[.45,.72,'#f7f5ef']];hubs.forEach((hub,hi)=>{pts.push({x:w*hub[0],y:h*hub[1],vx:0,vy:0,r:4.2,c:hub[2],hub:true,group:hi});for(let i=0;i<14;i++){const a=Math.random()*Math.PI*2,rad=28+Math.random()*72;pts.push({x:w*hub[0]+Math.cos(a)*rad,y:h*hub[1]+Math.sin(a)*rad,vx:(Math.random()-.5)*.45,vy:(Math.random()-.5)*.45,r:1.4+Math.random()*1.7,c:hub[2],group:hi})}})}function draw(){ctx.clearRect(0,0,w,h);ctx.globalCompositeOperation='source-over';pts.forEach((p,i)=>{p.x+=p.vx+Math.sin(Date.now()/900+i)*.045;p.y+=p.vy+Math.cos(Date.now()/800+i)*.045;if(p.x<16||p.x>w-16)p.vx*=-1;if(p.y<16||p.y>h-24)p.vy*=-1});for(let i=0;i<pts.length;i++){for(let j=i+1;j<pts.length;j++){const a=pts[i],b=pts[j],d=Math.hypot(a.x-b.x,a.y-b.y);if(d<95&&(a.group===b.group||d<54)){ctx.globalAlpha=Math.max(.04,.24-d/430);ctx.strokeStyle=a.group===b.group?'#d9d9d9':'#8d8d8d';ctx.lineWidth=a.hub||b.hub?.75:.45;ctx.beginPath();ctx.moveTo(a.x,a.y);ctx.lineTo(b.x,b.y);ctx.stroke()}}}pts.forEach(p=>{ctx.globalAlpha=p.hub?.9:.72;ctx.fillStyle=p.c;ctx.beginPath();ctx.arc(p.x,p.y,p.r,0,Math.PI*2);ctx.fill();if(p.hub){ctx.globalAlpha=.16;ctx.beginPath();ctx.arc(p.x,p.y,34,0,Math.PI*2);ctx.fill()}});requestAnimationFrame(draw)}addEventListener('resize',reset);reset();draw()}initMiniGraph();
const summaries={projects:['Projects','Public portfolio cases showing healthcare, machine learning, SQL, graphs, NLP and decision-oriented communication.'],methodtab:['Method','Practical data workflow: frame the decision, audit the data, build the analytical layer, choose the method and communicate limitations.'],stack:['Stack','Tools used across the projects: Python, SQL, Pandas, Power BI, Scikit-learn, NetworkX, NLP and dashboards.'],background:['Background','Career layer behind the projects: healthcare, Biomedical Engineering, Hospital Management, EBSERH/HC-UFU and marketing technology.']};function setTab(id){document.querySelectorAll('.tabbtn').forEach(b=>b.classList.toggle('active',b.dataset.tab===id));document.querySelectorAll('.panel').forEach(p=>p.classList.toggle('active',p.id===id));tabTitle.textContent=summaries[id][0];tabText.textContent=summaries[id][1]}document.querySelectorAll('.tabbtn').forEach(btn=>btn.addEventListener('click',()=>setTab(btn.dataset.tab)));contactForm.addEventListener('submit',async e=>{e.preventDefault();const btn=e.target.querySelector('button');btn.textContent='Sending...';const data={name:name.value,company:company.value,email:email.value,message:message.value};try{const r=await fetch('/api/contact',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify(data)});if(!r.ok)throw new Error('send failed');btn.textContent='Sent ✓';e.target.reset()}catch(err){btn.textContent='Error — try email';location.href='mailto:luandarodrigues30@gmail.com'}});const canvas=graphCanvas,ctx=canvas.getContext('2d'),stage=cloudStage;let W=0,H=0,dpr=1,nodes=[],edges=[],mode='cluster';const groups=[{name:'health',color:'#d7ff6f',cx:.25,cy:.32,count:innerWidth<520?28:70,labels:['healthcare','public health','HC-UFU','EBSERH','clinical pharmacy','UBS','SUS','geodata']},{name:'models',color:'#ff7777',cx:.72,cy:.34,count:innerWidth<520?26:62,labels:['machine learning','Scikit-learn','ROC-AUC','NLP','TF-IDF','reviews','risk']},{name:'ops',color:'#9fc8ff',cx:.55,cy:.72,count:innerWidth<520?30:74,labels:['Power BI','SQL','dashboards','KPIs','ETL','Pandas','operations']}];function resize(){dpr=Math.min(devicePixelRatio||1,2);W=stage.clientWidth;H=stage.clientHeight;canvas.width=W*dpr;canvas.height=H*dpr;canvas.style.width=W+'px';canvas.style.height=H+'px';ctx.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0)}function build(){resize();nodes=[];edges=[];let id=0;groups.forEach(g=>{let hub={id:id++,group:g.name,color:g.color,label:g.name,x:W*g.cx,y:H*g.cy,tx:W*g.cx,ty:H*g.cy,r:7,hub:true};nodes.push(hub);g.labels.forEach(l=>nodes.push({id:id++,group:g.name,color:g.color,label:l,x:W*(g.cx+(Math.random()-.5)*.25),y:H*(g.cy+(Math.random()-.5)*.25),r:3.6,major:true}));for(let i=0;i<g.count;i++)nodes.push({id:id++,group:g.name,color:g.color,label:'',x:W*(g.cx+(Math.random()-.5)*.35),y:H*(g.cy+(Math.random()-.5)*.35),r:1.7+Math.random()*1.8})});nodes.forEach(a=>{let same=nodes.filter(n=>n.group===a.group&&n.id!==a.id);for(let k=0;k<(a.hub?18:a.major?4:1);k++)edges.push([a,same[Math.floor(Math.random()*same.length)]]);if(Math.random()<.14){let b=nodes[Math.floor(Math.random()*nodes.length)];if(b.group!==a.group)edges.push([a,b])}});setTargets('cluster')}function setTargets(kind){mode=kind;groups.forEach(g=>{let list=nodes.filter(n=>n.group===g.name),cx=W*g.cx,cy=H*g.cy;list.forEach((n,i)=>{if(kind==='cluster'){let ang=i*.62,rad=n.hub?0:(n.major?45+Math.random()*50:70+Math.random()*Math.min(W,H)*.22);n.tx=cx+Math.cos(ang)*rad;n.ty=cy+Math.sin(ang)*rad}else{let ang=Math.random()*Math.PI*2,rad=Math.sqrt(Math.random())*Math.min(W,H)*.42;n.tx=W*.5+Math.cos(ang)*rad;n.ty=H*.52+Math.sin(ang)*rad}})})}function draw(){ctx.clearRect(0,0,W,H);nodes.forEach(n=>{n.x+=(n.tx-n.x)*.05;n.y+=(n.ty-n.y)*.05;n.x+=Math.sin(Date.now()/900+n.id)*.08;n.y+=Math.cos(Date.now()/1000+n.id)*.08});ctx.lineWidth=.65;edges.forEach(([a,b])=>{let d=Math.hypot(a.x-b.x,a.y-b.y);if(d<240){ctx.globalAlpha=Math.max(.03,.22-d/1000);ctx.strokeStyle='#9a9a9a';ctx.beginPath();ctx.moveTo(a.x,a.y);ctx.lineTo(b.x,b.y);ctx.stroke()}});nodes.forEach(n=>{ctx.globalAlpha=n.hub?.95:n.major?.82:.65;ctx.fillStyle=n.hub?'#d8d8d8':n.color;ctx.beginPath();ctx.arc(n.x,n.y,n.r,0,Math.PI*2);ctx.fill();if(n.major||n.hub){ctx.globalAlpha=.62;ctx.font=(n.hub?'700 12px ':'500 10px ')+'IBM Plex Mono';ctx.fillStyle='#d7d7d7';ctx.fillText(n.label,n.x+8,n.y-8)}});requestAnimationFrame(draw)}stage.addEventListener('click',()=>setTargets(mode==='cluster'?'spread':'cluster'));shuffleCloud.addEventListener('click',()=>setTargets('spread'));clusterCloud.addEventListener('click',()=>setTargets('cluster'));addEventListener('resize',()=>{resize();setTargets(mode)});build();draw();if(window.gsap){gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);gsap.to('.reveal',{opacity:1,y:0,duration:.9,stagger:.12,ease:'power3.out'});gsap.utils.toArray('.card,.box,.about-photo').forEach(el=>gsap.from(el,{opacity:0,y:22,duration:.6,ease:'power2.out',scrollTrigger:{trigger:el,start:'top 88%'}}))}
</script></body></html>